  Discord: `<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 00-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 00-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 00-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 00-.617-1.25.077.077 0 00-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 003.677 4.37a.07.07 0 00-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057c.002.022.015.04.03.05a19.9 19.9 0 005.993 3.03.078.078 0 00.084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 001.226-1.994.076.076 0 00-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 01-1.872-.892.077.077 0 01-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 00.372-.292.074.074 0 01.077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 01.078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 01-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 01-1.873.892.077.077 0 00-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 00.084.028 19.839 19.839 0 006.002-3.03.077.077 0 00.032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 00-.031-.03z"/></svg>`,
